{"tid":1578493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊既行動整合同少少建議","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T03:44:47.000Z","uid":48667,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7d0141c0a220cd9fb357b9a5137b5cd6645601","tid":1578493,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"見到行動post 少左好多,<br />\n想做返個簡單既整合, 歡迎補充, 希望大家唔好tl;dr <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一﹑行動timeline (9.18 - 10.1)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.18 </span></span><br />\n19:30 維園 【香港之路-球迷大和解】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.19</span></span><br />\n沙田聯校人鏈<br />\nWinter on fire 放映會 (各區開始時間唔同)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.20</span></span><br />\n12:00 UST 人鏈<br />\n17:00 荃灣中學生人鏈<br />\n22:00 太古城中心 【全民運動日】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.21</span></span><br />\n13:00 機場壓力測試 (未知行動詳情)<br />\n15:00 屯門公園再光復<br />\n19:00 元朗西鐵站 721兩個月 靜坐行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.22</span></span><br />\n12:00 新城市,連城廣場 【沙田罷買】<br />\n12:30 機場【和你suck 4.0】 (行動詳情當日公布, 好似話集中係青衣個邊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.28</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雨革五週年</span> <br />\n未有行動詳情<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9.29</span></span><br />\n【929全球抗赤納粹集會】<br />\n暫時未有行動詳情<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全港賀佢老母</span><br />\n大家都知, 但都未有行動詳情<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二﹑建議</span></span><br />\n首先就梗係希望未有行動細節既活動,<br />\n有左個方向俾大家先,<br />\n我知大家係廢事俾mon post 狗知道太多細節,但至少自己人都知自己要準備啲咩<br />\n同埋都係個句, 要宣傳俾同溫層以外既人知先易成事<br />\n<br />\n其次就係留意到大家都好關心831 當晚既真相,<br />\n消失左3個人都係靠唔少連登仔既摩擦力, <br />\n但我想提醒大家, 831 以黎發現咁多既疑點, <br />\n都係基於一啲已知既事實再發掘出黎, 而唔係靠一啲謠言或者9up<br />\n<br />\n尋晚高秀蘭單野, 其實都係靠巴打們既摩擦力同埋已知既事實再推測,<br />\n我認為呢啲係好既, 但唔好隨便話係核彈<br />\n當然, 後來有人fc 左其實唔係同一個人<br />\n咁就唔應該spin 左去其他謠言或者陰謀論到,<br />\n點知唔繼續關注返已經confirm 左既疑點呢? <br />\n<br />\n其實有可能大家已經愈黎愈接近真相,<br />\n所以先愈黎愈多呢啲無根據既傳言去掩飾真相<br />\n希望大家繼續關注831, 同埋新屋嶺,甚至其他俾人濫暴行私刑既義士,<br />\n專注搞好未來既行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0b536228c0eaa524147fc57c6d1f04ae3d86839","tid":1578493,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=803e50e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"b81abfb82cf51b36dc0d95a3e2592d666683021d","tid":1578493,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc